# CLAUDE.md

This file provides guidance to Claude Code when working with this repository.

## Stack

| Layer | Technology | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 15 (App Router) | Strict TypeScript, server components by default |
| Language | TypeScript 5.7+ | `noUncheckedIndexedAccess`, `exactOptionalPropertyTypes` |
| Auth | Clerk (web) + JWT (mobile) | Dual-mode — see Auth Architecture below |
| Database | Neon (serverless Postgres) | Drizzle ORM, push migrations |
| Rate Limiting | Upstash Redis | Sliding window, per-IP and per-user |
| Background Jobs | Inngest | Event-driven, opt-in |
| Payments | Stripe | Opt-in — gracefully skips when unconfigured |
| Storage | Cloudflare R2 | Opt-in — gracefully skips when unconfigured |
| Email | Resend | Opt-in — logs instead of sending when unconfigured |
| Hosting | Vercel | Preview deploys per branch, edge runtime for health check |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 3 | `cn()` helper via clsx + tailwind-merge |
| Testing | Vitest (unit), Playwright (E2E) | Strict CI: type-check + lint + test on every PR |
| Mobile | Flutter (Riverpod, GoRouter, Dio) | TODO: Remove if no mobile companion |

